#: app/settings.php:44
msgid "Provides PDF invoices and shipping labels for easy printing. Also generates barcodes for orders and product SKUs inside the WooCommerce dashboard, allowing you to scan them with the Hippoo WooCommerce app's barcode scanner to quickly find orders and products."
